EN: Her strong opinions make her stand out in the team.

ZH: 公司需要有主见的人来带领团队，决策才能更加远见。
EN: The company needs someone decisive to lead the team so that decisions can be more forward-thinking.

ZH: 在面对挑战时，坚持自己的主见很重要。
EN: It is important to stick to your own opinions when facing challenges.
